  {"word":"enthusiasm","pos":"n","ja":"熱意","level":3,"cat":"general","ipa":"/ɪnˈθuːziæzəm/","ex":"The students showed great enthusiasm for the robotics project.","exJa":"生徒たちはロボット製作にとても熱意を示した。","collocations":["show enthusiasm","with enthusiasm"],"synonyms":["passion","excitement"],"distractorHint":["疲労","無関心","恐怖"]},
