  {"word":"establish","pos":"v","ja":"確立する、設立する","level":3,"cat":"general","ipa":"/ɪˈstæblɪʃ/","ex":"The team established a clear testing schedule.","exJa":"チームは明確なテストスケジュールを確立した。","collocations":["establish a rule","establish trust"],"synonyms":["set up","found"],"distractorHint":["廃止する","破壊する","疑う"]},
