  {"word":"fair","pos":"adj","ja":"公平な","level":3,"cat":"general","ipa":"/fer/","ex":"The referee made sure the match was fair for both teams.","exJa":"審判は両チームにとって試合が公平であるようにした。","collocations":["fair play","fair judgment"],"synonyms":["just","impartial"],"distractorHint":["不利な","厳しい","有名な"]},
  {"word":"familiar","pos":"adj","ja":"よく知っている、馴染みの","level":3,"cat":"general","ipa":"/fəˈmɪljər/","ex":"Are you familiar with this programming language?","exJa":"あなたはこのプログラミング言語をよく知っていますか。","collocations":["familiar with","become familiar"],"synonyms":["acquainted","known"],"distractorHint":["珍しい","苦手な","不安な"]},
  {"word":"feasible","pos":"adj","ja":"実行可能な","level":3,"cat":"general","ipa":"/ˈfiːzəbəl/","ex":"Is it feasible to finish the design by next week?","exJa":"来週までにデザインを終えるのは実行可能ですか。","collocations":["feasible plan","technically feasible"],"synonyms":["viable","achievable"],"distractorHint":["不可能な","危険な","理想的な"]},
  {"word":"feature","pos":"n","ja":"特徴、機能","level":3,"cat":"general","ipa":"/ˈfiːtʃər/","ex":"This new feature allows the arm to rotate 360 degrees.","exJa":"この新しい機能によりアームは360度回転できる。","collocations":["key feature","main feature"],"synonyms":["characteristic","function"],"distractorHint":["欠陥","制限","価格"]},
  {"word":"fierce","pos":"adj","ja":"激しい、猛烈な","level":3,"cat":"general","ipa":"/fɪrs/","ex":"The competition between the two teams was fierce.","exJa":"二つのチーム間の競争は激しかった。","collocations":["fierce competition","fierce battle"],"synonyms":["intense","aggressive"],"distractorHint":["穏やかな","弱い","静かな"]},
  {"word":"firm","pos":"adj","ja":"固い、確固とした","level":3,"cat":"general","ipa":"/fɜːrm/","ex":"Make sure the bracket has a firm grip on the frame.","exJa":"ブラケットがフレームをしっかりと固定していることを確認して。","collocations":["firm grip","firm decision"],"synonyms":["solid","steady"],"distractorHint":["柔らかい","不安定な","一時的な"]},
  {"word":"flaw","pos":"n","ja":"欠陥","level":3,"cat":"general","ipa":"/flɔː/","ex":"They found a design flaw in the gripper mechanism.","exJa":"グリッパー機構に設計上の欠陥が見つかった。","collocations":["design flaw","fatal flaw"],"synonyms":["defect","fault"],"distractorHint":["利点","目的","部品"]},
