  {"word":"frequent","pos":"adj","ja":"頻繁な","level":3,"cat":"general","ipa":"/ˈfriːkwənt/","ex":"We hold frequent meetings to track our progress.","exJa":"私たちは進捗を確認するために頻繁に会議を開く。","collocations":["frequent visits","frequent breaks"],"synonyms":["recurring","regular"],"distractorHint":["稀な","短い","重要な"]},
