  {"word":"generous","pos":"adj","ja":"気前の良い、寛大な","level":3,"cat":"general","ipa":"/ˈdʒenərəs/","ex":"The sponsor was generous enough to donate new motors.","exJa":"そのスポンサーは新しいモーターを寄付するほど気前が良かった。","collocations":["generous donation","generous offer"],"synonyms":["charitable","giving"],"distractorHint":["けちな","冷たい","慎重な"]},
