  {"word":"goal","pos":"n","ja":"目標","level":3,"cat":"general","ipa":"/ɡoʊl/","ex":"Our main goal this season is to qualify for the finals.","exJa":"今シーズンの主な目標は決勝進出だ。","collocations":["set a goal","achieve a goal"],"synonyms":["objective","target"],"distractorHint":["結果","障害","規則"]},
